quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  26,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  26,1,Taa-Seeen-Meeem
  26,2,yeh kitaab roshan ki ayatain hain
  26,3,( ae peghamber ) shayad tum is ( ranj ) se ke yeh log imaan nahi laatay apne tain halaak kardo ge
  26,4,agar hum chahain to un par aasman se nishani utaar den. phir un ki gardanein is ke agay jhuk jayen
  26,5,aur un ke paas ( khuday-e ) rehman ki taraf se koi nasiyaat nahi aati magar yeh is se munh phair letay hain
  26,6,so yeh to jhutla chuke ab un ko is cheez ki haqeeqat maloom hogi jis ki hansi uratye they
  26,7,kiya unhon ne zameen ki taraf nahi dekha ke hum ne is mein har qisam ki kitni nafees cheezein ugai hain
  26,8,kuch shak nahi ke is mein ( qudrat khuda ki ) nishani hai magar yeh aksar imaan laane walay nahi hain
  26,9,aur tumhara perwar-digaar ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai
  26,10,aur jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne moose ko puraka ke zalim logon ke paas jao
  26,11,"( yani ) qoum firaon ke paas,kiya yeh drtay nahi"
  26,12,unhon ne kaha ke mere perwar-digaar mein darta hon ke yeh mujhe jhoota samjhain
  26,13,aur mera dil tang hota hai aur meri zabaan rukti hai to Haroon ko hukum bhaij ke mere sath chalein
  26,14,aur un logon ka mujh par aik gunah ( yani qabti ke khoon ka daawa ) bhi hai so mujhe yeh bhi khauf hai ke mujh ko maar hi dalain
  26,15,farmaya hargiz nahi. tum dono hamari nishanain le kar jao hum tumahray sath suneney walay hain
  26,16,to dono firaon ke paas jao aur kaho ke hum tamam Jahan ke maalik ke beje hue hain
  26,17,( aur is liye aeye hain ) ke aap bani Israel ko hamaray sath jaane ki ijazat den
  26,18,( firaon ne moose se kaha )kiya hum ne tum ko ke abhi bachay they parwarish nahikiya aur tum ne barson hamaray haan Umar busr ( nahi ) ki
  26,19,aur tum ne woh kaamkiya tha jokiya aur tum nashukray maloom hotay ho
  26,20,( moose ne ) kahan ( haan ) woh harkat mujh se nagahan sarzad hui thi aur mein khata karon mein tha
  26,21,to jab mujhe tum se dar laga to tum mein se bhaag gaya. phir khuda ne mujh ko nabuwat وعلم bakhsha aur mujhe payghambaroon mein sekiya
  26,22,aur (kiya ) yahi ahsaan hai jo aap mujh par rakhtay hain ke aap ne bani Israel ko ghulam bana rakha hai
  26,23,firaon ne kaha ke tamam Jahan maalikkiya
  26,24,kaha ke asmano aur zameen aur jo kuch un dono mein hai sab ka maalik. bashart e kay tum logon ko yaqeen ho
  26,25,firaon ne apne ا aahali mawali se kaha kekiya tum suntay nahi
  26,26,( moose ne ) kaha ke tumhara aur tumahray pehlay baap dada ka maalik
  26,27,( firaon ne ) kaha ke ( yeh ) paighambar jo tumhari taraf bheja gaya hai bawla hai
  26,28,"moose ne kaha ke mashriq aur maghrib aur jo kuch un dono mein hai sab ka maalik, bashart e kay tum ko samajh ho"
  26,29,( firaon ne ) kaha ke agar tum ne mere siwa kisi aur ko mabood banaya to mein tumhe qaid kardoon ga
  26,30,( moose ne ) kaha khuwa mein aap ke paas roshan cheez lau ( yani moujza )
  26,31,firaon ne kaha agar sachey ho to usay lao ( dikhao )
  26,32,pas unhon ne apni laathi daali to woh isi waqt Sarih اasdaha ban gayi
  26,33,aur apna haath nikala to isi dam dekhnay walon ke liye safaid ( Buraq nazar anay laga )
  26,34,firaon ne apne gird ke sardaro se kaha ke yeh to kaamil fun jadugar hai
  26,35,chahta hai ke tum ko apne jaadoo ( ke zor ) se tumahray malik se nikaal day to tumharikiya raye hai ?
  26,36,unhon ne kaha ke usay aur is ke bhai ( ke baray ) mein kuch tawaquf kijiye aur shehron mein hrkare bhaij dijiye
  26,37,ke sab maahir gado garon ko ( jama karkay ) aap ke paas le ayen
  26,38,to jadugar aik muqarara din ki meyaad par jama hogaye
  26,39,aur logon se keh diya gaya ke tum ( sab ) ko ikhatay ho kar jana chahiye
  26,40,taakay agar jadugar ghalib rahen to hum un ke pairo ho jaien
  26,41,jab jadugar aagaye to firaon se kehnay lagey agar hum ghalib rahay to hamein sila bhi ataa hoga ?
  26,42,firaon ne kaha haan aur tum muqarabon mein bhi daakhil karliye jao ge
  26,43,"moose ne un se kaha ke jo cheez dalni chahtay ho, daalo"
  26,44,to unhon ne apni rasiyaan aur lathyan dalain aur kehnay lagey ke firaon ke Iqbal ki qasam hum zaroor ghalib rahen ge
  26,45,phir moose ne apni laathi daali to woh un cheezon ko jo gado garonne banai theen yakayak nighalnay lagi
  26,46,tab jadugar sjday mein gir parre
  26,47,( aur ) kehnay lagey ke hum tamam Jahan ke maalik par imaan le aeye
  26,48,jo moose aur Haroon ka maalik hai
  26,49,"firaon ne kahakiya is se pehlay ke mein tum ko ijazat dun tum is par imaan le aeye, be shak yeh tumhara bara hai jis ne tum ko jaadoo sikhaya hai. so anqareeb tum ( is ka injaam ) maloom karlo ge ke mein tumahray haath aur paon atraaf mukhalif se ktwa dun ga aur tum sab ko suli par chrhhwa dun ga"
  26,50,unhon ne kaha ke kuch nuqsaan ( ki baat ) nahi hum apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout jaane walay hain
  26,51,hamein umeed hai ke hamara perwar-digaar hamaray gunah bakhash day ga. is liye ke hum awwal imaan laane walon mein hain
  26,52,aur hum ne moose ki taraf wahi bhaije ke hamaray bundon ko raat ko le niklo ke ( firounion ki taraf se ) tumhara taqubkiya jaye ga
  26,53,to firaon ne shehron mein naqeeb ravnh kiye
  26,54,( aur kaha ) ke yeh log thori si jamaat hai
  26,55,aur yeh hamein gussa dila rahay hain
  26,56,aur hum sab ba-sazo- samaan hain
  26,57,to hum ne un ko baghoon aur chashmon se nikaal diya
  26,58,aur khazanon aur nafees makanaat se
  26,59,( un ke sath hum ne ) is terhan (kiya ) aur un cheezon ka waris bani Israel ko kar diya
  26,60,to unhon ne Sooraj nikaltay ( yani subah ko ) un ka taqubkiya
  26,61,jab dono jamaten aamnay samnay huien to moose ke saathi kehnay lagey ke hum to pakar liye gay
  26,62,moose ne kaha hargiz nahi mera perwar-digaar mere sath hai woh mujhe rasta betaye ga
  26,63,is waqt hum ne moose ki taraf wahi bhaije ke apni laathi darya par maro. to darya phatt gaya. aur har aik tukda ( yun ) hogaya ( ke ) goya bara pahar ( hai )
  26,64,aur dosaron ko wahan hum ne qareeb kardiya
  26,65,aur moose aur un ke sath walon ko to bacha liya
  26,66,phir dosaron ko duubo diya
  26,67,be shak is ( qissay ) mein nishani hai. lekin yeh aksar imaan laane walay nahi
  26,68,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai
  26,69,aur un ko ibrahim ka haal parh kar suna do
  26,70,jab unhon ne apne baap aur apni qoum ke logon se kaha ke tum kis cheez ko pujte ho
  26,71,woh kehnay lagey ke hum buton ko pujte hain aur un ki pooja par qaim hain
  26,72,ibrahim ne kaha ke jab tum un ko pkarte ho tokiya woh tumhari aawaz ko suntay hain ?
  26,73,ya tumhe kuch faiday day satke ya nuqsaan pouncha satke hain ?
  26,74,unhon ne kaha ( nahi ) balkay hum ne apne baap dada ko isi terhan karte dekha hai
  26,75,ibrahim ne kahakiya tum ne dekha ke jin ko tum pujte rahay ho
  26,76,tum bhi aur tumahray aglay baap dada bhi
  26,77,woh mere dushman hain. magar khuday-e rab alameen ( mera dost hai )
  26,78,jis ne mujhe pedakiya hai aur wohi mujhe rasta dekhata hai
  26,79,aur woh jo mujhe khelata aur plata hai
  26,80,aur jab mein bemaar parta hon to mujhe Shifa bakhshta hai
  26,81,aur jo mujhe maaray ga aur phir zindah kere ga
  26,82,aur woh jis se mein umeed rakhta hon ke qayamat ke din mere gunah bakhshay ga
  26,83,ae perwar-digaar mujhe ilm o danish ataa farma aur naiko karon mein shaamil kar
  26,84,aur pichlle logon mein mera zikar naik ( jari ) kar
  26,85,aur mujhe Nemat ki bahisht ke varson mein kar
  26,86,aur mere baap ko bakhash day ke woh gumrahon mein se hai
  26,87,aur jis din log utha kharray kiye jayen ge mujhe ruswa nah kejio
  26,88,jis din nah maal hi kuch faida day saka ga aur nah betay
  26,89,haan jo shakhs khuda ke paas pak dil le kar aaya ( woh bach jaye ga )
  26,90,aur bahisht parhaiz garon ke qareeb kar di jaye gi
  26,91,aur dozakh gumrahon ke samnay layi jaye gi
  26,92,aur un se kaha jaye ga ke jin ko tum pujte they woh kahan hain ?
  26,93,yani jin ko khuda ke siwa ( pujte they )kiya woh tumhari madad kar saktay hain ya khud badla le satke hain
  26,94,to woh aur gumraah ( yani buut aur buut parast ) avndhe munh dozakh mein daal diye jayen ge
  26,95,aur shetan ke lashkar sab ke sab ( daakhil jahannum hon ge )
  26,96,woh aapas mein jhagrain ge aur kahin ge
  26,97,ke khuda ki qasam hum to Sarih gumraahi mein they
  26,98,jab ke tumhe ( khuday-e ) rab alameen ke barabar th_hrate they
  26,99,aur hum ko un gunahgaaron hi ne gumraahkiya tha
  26,100,to ( aaj ) nah koi hamara sifarish karne wala hai
  26,101,aur nah garam josh dost
  26,102,kash hamein ( duniya mein ) phir jana ho tum hum mominon mein ho jaien
  26,103,be shak is mein nishani hai aur un mein aksar imaan laane walay nahi
  26,104,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib aur meharban hai
  26,105,qoum Nooh ne bhi payghambaroon ko jhtlaya
  26,106,jab un se un ke bhai Nooh ne kaha ke tum drtay kyun nahi
  26,107,mein to tumhara amanat daar hon
  26,108,to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  26,109,aur is kaam ka tum se kuch sila nahi mangta. mera sila to khuday-e rab alameen hi par hai
  26,110,to khuda se daro aur mere kehnay par chalo
  26,111,woh bolay kekiya hum tum ko maan len aur tumahray pairo to razeel log hotay hain
  26,112,Nooh ne kaha ke mujhekiya maloom ke wohkiya karte hain
  26,113,un ka hisaab ( aamaal ) mere perwar-digaar ke zimmay hai kash tum samjhoo
  26,114,aur mein mominon ko nikaal dainay wala nahi hon
  26,115,mein to sirf khol khol kar nasiyaat karne wala hon
  26,116,unhon ne kaha ke Nooh agar tum baz nah aao ge to sangsar kardiye jao ge
  26,117,Nooh ne kaha ke perwar-digaar meri qoum ne to mujhe jhutla diya
  26,118,so to mere aur un ke darmain aik khula faisla kardey aur mujhe aur jo mere sath hain un ko bacha le
  26,119,"pas hum ne un ko aur jo un ke sath kashti mein sawaar they, un ko bacha liya"
  26,120,phir is ke baad baqi logon ko duubo diya
  26,121,be shak is mein nishani hai aur un mein aksar imaan laane walay nahi they
  26,122,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai
  26,123,Aad ne bhi payghambaroon ko jhtlaya
  26,124,jab un se un ke bhai Hood ne kahakiya tum drtay nahi
  26,125,mein to tumhara amanat daar paighambar hon
  26,126,to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  26,127,aur mein is ka tum se kuch badla nahi mangta. mera badla ( khuday-e ) rab alameen ke zimmay hai
  26,128,bhala tum har onche jagah par nishaan taamer karte ho
  26,129,aur mehal banatay ho shayad tum hamesha raho ge
  26,130,aur jab ( kisi ko ) pakarte ho to zalimana pakarte ho
  26,131,to khuda se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,132,aur is se jis ne tum ko un cheezon se madad di jin ko tum jantay ho. daro
  26,133,is ne tumhe charpayon aur beton se madad di
  26,134,aur baghoon aur chashmon se
  26,135,mujh ko tumahray baray mein barray ( sakht ) din ke azaab ka khauf hai
  26,136,woh kehnay lagey ke hamein khuwa nasiyaat karo ya nah karo hamaray liye yaksaa hai
  26,137,yeh to uglo hi ke tareeq hain
  26,138,aur hum par koi azaab nahi aeye ga
  26,139,to unhon ne Hood ko jhtlaya to hum ne un ko halaak kar dala. be shak is mein nishani hai. aur un mein aksar imaan laane walay nahi they
  26,140,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib aur meharban hai
  26,141,( aur ) qoum smod ne bhi payghambaroon ko jhutla diya
  26,142,jab un se un ke bhai Saleh ne kaha ke tum drtay kyun nahi ?
  26,143,mein to tumhara amanat daar hon
  26,144,to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  26,145,aur mein is ka tum se badla nahi mangta. mera badla ( khuda ) rab alameen ke zimmay hai
  26,146,kiya woh cheezein ( tumhe yahan muyassar ) hain un mein tum be khauf chore diye jao ge
  26,147,( yani ) baagh aur chashmay
  26,148,aur khityan aur khjorin jin ke khoshay lateef wa nazuk hotay hain
  26,149,aur takalouf se pahoron mein taraash kharaash kar ghar banatay ho
  26,150,to khuda se daro aur mere kehnay par chalo
  26,151,aur hadd se tajawaz karne walon ki baat nah manu
  26,152,jo malik mein fasaad karte hain aur islaah nahi karte
  26,153,woh kehnay lagey ke tum to jaadoo zada ho
  26,154,tum aur kuch nahi hamari terhan aadmi ho. agar sachey ho to koi nishani paish karo
  26,155,Saleh ne kaha ( dekho ) yeh oontni hai ( aik din ) is ki pani peenay ki baari hai aur aik Moueen roz tumhari baari
  26,156,aur is ko koi takleef nah dena ( nahi to ) tum ko sakht azaab aa pakdae ga
  26,157,to unhon ne is ki koncheen kaat dalain phir nadim hue
  26,158,so un ko azaab ne aan pakra. be shak is mein nishani hai. aur un mein aksar imaan laane walay nahi they
  26,159,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai
  26,160,( aur qoum ) Loot ne bhi payghambaroon ko jhtlaya
  26,161,jab un se un ke bhai Loot ne kaha ke tum kyun nahi drtay ?
  26,162,mein to tumhara amanat daar paighambar hon
  26,163,to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  26,164,aur mein tum se is ( kaam ) ka badla nahi mangta. mera badla ( khuday-e ) rab alameen ke zimmay hai
  26,165,kiya tum ahal aalam mein se larkoon par mael hotay ho
  26,166,aur tumahray perwar-digaar ne jo tumahray liye tumhari biwiyan peda ki hain un ko chore dete ho. haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum hadd se nikal jaane walay ho
  26,167,woh kehnay lagey ke Loot agar tum baz nah aao ge to shehar badar kardiye jao ge
  26,168,Loot ne kaha ke mein tumahray kaam ka sakht dushman hon
  26,169,ae mere perwar-digaar mujh ko aur mere ghar walon ko un ke kamon ( ke wabaal ) se nijaat day
  26,170,so hum ne un ko aur un ke ghar walon ko sab ko nijaat di
  26,171,magar aik budiya ke peechay reh gayi
  26,172,phir hum ne ouron ko halaak kardiya
  26,173,aur un parmeinhہ barsaya. so jomeinhہ un ( logon ) par ( barsa ) jo dry gay bura tha
  26,174,be shak is mein nishani hai. aur un mein aksar imaan laane walay nahi they
  26,175,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai .
  26,176,aur ban ke rehne walon ne bhi payghambaroon ko jhtlaya
  26,177,jab un se Shoiab ne kaha ke tum drtay kyun nahi ?
  26,178,mein to tumhara amanat daar paighambar hon
  26,179,to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  26,180,aur mein is kaam ka tum se kuch badla nahi mangta mera badla to khuday-e rab alameen ke zimmay hai
  26,181,( dekho ) pemana poora bhara karo aur nuqsaan nahkiya karo
  26,182,aur traazo seedhi rakh kar tola karo
  26,183,aur logon ko un ki cheezein kam nah diya karo aur malik mein fasaad nah karte phiro
  26,184,aur is se daro jis ne tum ko aur pehli khalqat ko pedakiya
  26,185,woh kehnay lagey ke tum jaadoo zada ho
  26,186,aur tum aur kuch nahi hum hi jaisay aadmi ho. aur hamara khayaal hai ke tum jhutay ho
  26,187,aur agar sachey ho to hum par aasman se aik tukda laa kar girao
  26,188,Shoiab ne kaha ke jo kaam tum karte ho mera perwar-digaar is se khoob waaqif hai
  26,189,"to un logon ne un ko jhtlaya, pas saibaan ke azaab ne un ko aa pakra. be shak woh barray ( sakht ) din ka azaab tha"
  26,190,is mein yaqeenan nishani hai. aur un mein aksar imaan laane walay nahi they
  26,191,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai
  26,192,aur yeh quran ( khuday-e ) perwar-digaar aalam ka utaara howa hai
  26,193,is ko amanat daar farishta le kar utra hai
  26,194,( yani is ne ) tumahray dil par ( alqa )kiya hai taakay ( logon ko ) nasiyaat karte raho
  26,195,aur ( alqa bhi ) Fasih arabi zabaan mein (kiya hai )
  26,196,aur is ki khabar pehlay payghambaroon ki kitabon mein ( likhi hui ) hai
  26,197,kiya un ke liye yeh sanad nahi hai ke ulmaye bani Israel is ( baat ) ko jantay hain
  26,198,aur agar hum is ko kisi ghair ahal zabaan par utaartay
  26,199,aur woh usay un ( logon ko ) parh kar sunataa to yeh usay ( kabhi ) nah mantay
  26,200,isi terhan hum ne inkaar ko gunahgaaron ke dilon mein daakhil kardiya
  26,201,"woh jab taq dard dainay wala azaab nah dekh len ge, is ko nahi manen ge"
  26,202,woh un par nagahan aa waqay hoga aur inhen khabar bhi nah hogi
  26,203,is waqt kahin gekiya hamein mohlat miley gi ?
  26,204,tokiya yeh hamaray azaab ko jaldi talab kar rahay hain
  26,205,bhala dekho to agar hum un ko barson faiday dete rahay
  26,206,phir un par woh ( azaab ) aa waqay ho jis ka tum se wadakiya jata hai
  26,207,to jo faiday yeh uthatay rahay un ke kis kaam ayen ge
  26,208,aur hum ne koi bastii halaak nahi ki magar is ke liye nasiyaat karne walay ( pehlay bhaij dete ) they
  26,209,nasiyaat kar dein aur hum zalim nahi hain
  26,210,aur is ( quran ) ko shetan le kar nazil nahi hue
  26,211,yeh kaam nah to un ko sazawar hai aur nah woh is ki taaqat rakhtay hain
  26,212,woh ( aasmani baton ) ke suneney ( ke maqamat ) se allag kar diye gay hain
  26,213,"to khuda ke siwa kisi aur mabood ko mat pukarna, warna tum ko azaab diya jaye ga"
  26,214,aur apne qareeb ke rishta daaron ko dar suna do
  26,215,aur jo momin tumahray pairo hogaye hain un se mutwaza paish aao
  26,216,phir agar log tumhari nafarmani karen to keh do ke mein tumahray aamaal se be talluq hon
  26,217,aur ( khuday-e ) ghalib aur meharban par bhrosa rakho
  26,218,jo tum ko jab tum ( thajjud ) ke waqt uthte ho daikhta hai
  26,219,aur nmazyon mein tumahray phirnay ko bhi
  26,220,be shak woh suneney aur jan-nay wala hai
  26,221,( acha ) mein tmin batau ke shetan kis par utarte hain
  26,222,har jhutay gunehgaar par utarte hain
  26,223,jo suni hui baat ( is ke kaam mein ) laa daaltay hain aur woh aksar jhutay hain
  26,224,aur shayron ki pairwi gumraah logkiya karte hain
  26,225,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke woh har waadi mein sir maartay phirtay hain
  26,226,aur kehte woh hain jo karte nahi
  26,227,magar jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam kiye aur khuda ko bohat yaad karte rahay aur apne oopar zulm honay ke baad intiqam liya aur zalim anqareeb jaan len ge ke kon si jagah lout kar jatay hain
